org.sakaiproject.component.app.profile

Class LegacyProfileManagerImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.component.app.profile.LegacyProfileManagerImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ProfileManager

    public class LegacyProfileManagerImpl
extends Object
implements ProfileManager
    This is implementation of ProfileManager that is to be only used directly by the original Profile tool For all others, you must use the ProfileManager bean. See that class for info about how to swap out the implementation. It may be that you end up getting this implementation via proxy depending on your config, but don't use it directly.
